00:11:57,659 --> 00:12:00,923
I had to get that ass shot in there.

231
00:12:01,083 --> 00:12:01,443
Had to.

232
00:12:03,402 --> 00:12:04,763
Haven't seen enough of Mass Effect 3.

233
00:12:05,583 --> 00:12:07,545
There might be a more up-to-date Ashot

234
00:12:07,565 --> 00:12:09,346
that I could have put in there, but I didn't have time.

